data: {"type":"response.output_item.done","item":{"type":"a2a_preview_call_output","id":"fco_0d58545577010320006a15d928ef848197b5d7f5132464f756","agent_reference":{"type":"agent_reference","name":"cs-e2e-tests-client","version":"1"},"response_id":"resp_0d58545577010320006a15d90709f08197bcf766e6eff9109f","call_id":"call_a524b1a0c1164bd2adf7724d7287bfa1","name":"workiqc4k5h8","output":"You have **3 meetings scheduled for today**. Here’s your full agenda:\n\n---\n\n### ✅ 1. [DevEx Engineering: weekly meeting](https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkAGI4NTJlOTY2LWVhYTgtNDUwMy04MmFlLTBiOTFhY2EyYmI5NAFRAAgI3rq5ut3AAEYAAAAAxlcDfIcKC0iM2tlcAvavNgcAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QAAAAABDQAAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QAIOdCAHwAAEA%3d%3d&EntityRepresentationId=061539ea-7329-463b-87db-f7c267526073) 【1-c3eda9】  \n- **Time:** 4:05 PM – 5:00 PM  \n- **Organizer:** [Travis Wilson](https://www.office.com/search?q=Travis+Wilson&EntityRepresentationId=e7a256f5-3f47-41c3-b850-b6326e1a9c7a) 【1-c3eda9】  \n- **Location:** Microsoft Teams + Focus Room 16/1M03 / Conf Room 16/11 【1-c3eda9】  \n- **Status:** ✅ Already finished  \n\n---\n\n### ⏳ 2. [AI Foundry SDK/API Reviews](https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkAGI4NTJlOTY2LWVhYTgtNDUwMy04MmFlLTBiOTFhY2EyYmI5NAFRAAgI3rq5ut3AAEYAAAAAxlcDfIcKC0iM2tlcAvavNgcAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QAAAAABDQAAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QADjeEUBgAAEA%3d%3d&EntityRepresentationId=bd6930bb-875e-4cdc-aea2-f6b90650acfd) 【2-eae579】  \n- **Time:** 6:05 PM – 7:00 PM  \n- **Organizer:** [Dan Taylor](https://www.office.com/search?q=Dan+Taylor&EntityRepresentationId=c4bc5fa0-169e-4527-8ef2-f7e22df28faa) 【2-eae579】  \n- **Status:** Tentatively accepted  \n- **Note:** ⚠️ Conflicts with your team lunch  \n\n---\n\n### \uD83C\uDF7D️ 3. [Team Lunch](https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkAGI4NTJlOTY2LWVhYTgtNDUwMy04MmFlLTBiOTFhY2EyYmI5NAFRAAgI3rq5ut3AAEYAAAAAxlcDfIcKC0iM2tlcAvavNgcAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QAAAAABDQAAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QADjeFGvwAAEA%3d%3d&EntityRepresentationId=dae5d064-428b-4084-ab11-da39f3743c4f) 【3-5b652f】  \n- **Time:** 6:45 PM – 8:00 PM  \n- **Organizer:** [Travis Angevine](https://www.office.com/search?q=Travis+Angevine&EntityRepresentationId=0c82ffd0-2658-42b8-9b2a-1dbe79e000cd) 【3-5b652f】  \n- **Location:** Building 16 Lobby 【3-5b652f】  \n- **Attendees include:** your core team (e.g., [Darren Cohen](https://www.office.com/search?q=Darren+Cohen&EntityRepresentationId=6b0bd318-82fb-4616-b6ef-24f599e3e23f), [Howie Leung](https://www.office.com/search?q=Howie+Leung&EntityRepresentationId=4d57f35f-8327-4ae0-8d89-1e5ca72b7477), [Kaylie Leung](https://www.office.com/search?q=Kaylie+Leung&EntityRepresentationId=b6d49469-8c73-4027-a9cd-7e1fb4a9bfcf)) 【3-5b652f】  \n- **Note:** ⚠️ Overlaps with the SDK/API Reviews meeting  \n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ Conflict Summary\n- **6:05–7:00 PM:** [AI Foundry SDK/API Reviews](https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkAGI4NTJlOTY2LWVhYTgtNDUwMy04MmFlLTBiOTFhY2EyYmI5NAFRAAgI3rq5ut3AAEYAAAAAxlcDfIcKC0iM2tlcAvavNgcAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QAAAAABDQAAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QADjeEUBgAAEA%3d%3d&EntityRepresentationId=bd6930bb-875e-4cdc-aea2-f6b90650acfd)  \n- **6:45–8:00 PM:** [Team Lunch](https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meeting/details?eventId=AAMkAGI4NTJlOTY2LWVhYTgtNDUwMy04MmFlLTBiOTFhY2EyYmI5NAFRAAgI3rq5ut3AAEYAAAAAxlcDfIcKC0iM2tlcAvavNgcAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QAAAAABDQAAUK8J1_iHKU2PtUBJgHeK-QADjeFGvwAAEA%3d%3d&EntityRepresentationId=dae5d064-428b-4084-ab11-da39f3743c4f)  \n➡️ You’ll need to choose between these (or split attendance).\n\n---\n\nIf you want, I can help you **decide which meeting to prioritize** based on your recent work (e.g., Foundry SDK involvement vs. team syncs), or take an action like tentatively accepting/declining one.\n","status":"completed"},"output_index":1,"sequence_number":6}

